msgid "Themeable"
msgstr "Témovateľné"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Hundreds of levels"
msgstr "Stovky úrovní"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:21
msgid "Level-editor"
msgstr "Editor úrovne"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"Two modes for the enemies: classical and KGoldrunner-mode, in KGoldrunner-"
"mode they are more intelligent, in the classical mode it is easier to fool "
"them"
msgstr ""
"Dva modely pre nepriateľov: klasické a reťim KGoldRunner, v tomto režime sú "
"inteligentnejší, v klasickom režime je ľahšie ich zmiasť."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
